Text: Fair enough. Ik stuffs wrong and has been for a while. I don’t even care if I ever get diagnosed tbh, I just don’t want to be inaccurate about things :/

Author: sintos-compa
Text: don't bother pigeonholing yourself. if eating,rituals,dieting,culture around it is causing you enough frustration and distress where you start saying "this isn't right", something's wrong. having a diagnosed ED isn't a Scout's Badge.
